<P>
Photo, Atlanta catcher John Russell (6), chasing foul ball, slides into Braves' 
dugout. Also coming over are pitcher John Smoltz and first baseman Darrell 
Evans. Braves lost to Dodgers, 10-2. MARSHA TRAEGER / Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</GRAPHIC>
