<HEADLINE>
<P>
FOR THE RECORD 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Marvin Mitchelson -- A headline Friday incorrectly stated that attorney Marvin 
Mitchelson was absolved by a jury who heard a malpractice lawsuit filed against 
him by Felicia Gordon. The jury found that Mitchelson failed to use ordinary 
care and skill in handling her divorce case but it concluded that she was not 
damaged by his actions. The jury also found that Mitchelson did not 
intentionally or negligently inflict emotional distress on Gordon. 
</P>
</TEXT>
